{"tid":2395274,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸 復發一問 [有圖慎入]","createTime":"2021-02-04T19:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T10:55:17.000Z","uid":390850,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9b6d059093a728a847160e98f5f2bed172aaa4","tid":2395274,"uid":390850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T19:37:58.000Z","msg":"先講下背景，混合性皮膚偏油，<br />\n暗瘡由小六開始生由額頭到成臉都係，係試過所有方法［針清(千其唔好試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），中醫，去痘產品］所有方法我試得就試但全部都冇用，反而嚴重左。<br />\n最尾頂唔順走去睇西醫<br />\n<br />\n食左半年藥<br />\n食個陣冇爆發期<br />\n皮膚變左做乾性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概係完左藥年半多啲開始生返暗瘡<br />\n雖然都叫謝得快<br />\n但幾乎隔一兩日瞓醒就多左幾粒<br />\n基本上以加全臉都有暗瘡印同新瘡<br />\n同以前比係叫做唔嚴重多<br />\n但就無停過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔太清楚我以加呢種情況算唔算復發<br />\n有諗過關唔關戴口罩焗事<br />\n因為差唔多每次戴完口罩臉都會好痕同紅<br />\n<br />\n準備課金呢幾日去睇多次醫生<br />\n想知有冇巴絲都試過有類似情況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有圖慎入<br />\n<br />\n食A酸前：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCcJAfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCcJAfj.jpg&h=b7f60873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9ZoAfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9ZoAfj.jpg&h=7cb00ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱啱完藥一年:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bastMpR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbastMpR.png&h=073e3d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近：<br />\n下巴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqN9vMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqN9vMC.png&h=73b645ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩邊臉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bsmmUd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bsmmUd.png&h=e9105489&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqgFCsz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqgFCsz.png&h=75732c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爛過就十年嘅臉好得翻唔想再爛過<br />\n唔想再過望住塊鏡數每日多左幾多粒暗瘡勁崩潰嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望我可以真正成功斷到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企人到以加都仲係同我講我之所以生瘡係因為熱氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796ba15b7d84102e8321a7626a543b016ae659af","tid":2395274,"uid":25062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T19:48:45.000Z","msg":"復發味再食，不過少量咁食囉<br />\n<br />\n食夠都未必斷架，最多冇之前咁嚴重。<br />\n有啲人話食完之後冇再生，可能係因為都咁多年，青春期過咗面油都少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f75b81b76426a09465e77cd0ef984c02c61a2b","tid":2395274,"uid":154243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T20:34:51.000Z","msg":"係咪荷爾蒙問題呀？<br />\n我完咗A酸年半左右黎M前都會出痘<br />\n不過keep住搽A酸藥膏就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a2159d692633ac1cbf71d5b2ef4502fd37746a","tid":2395274,"uid":209522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T21:04:16.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪對奶/蛋個啲敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前個情況同你一樣 又係食完一段時間後復發<br />\n之後我去做左個IgG食物敏感測試<br />\n之後發現原來對奶/蛋類嚴重敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住就開始戒 半年後就好好多 <br />\n有時口痕會買杯奶茶飲 <br />\n第二日有機會生暗瘡 不過都係啲細粒野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比之前好左好多<br />\n建議樓主都可以試吓 起碼知道有咩食得有咩唔食得"},{"pid":"32f88d57abe32840dda9a3f487528c7a76ca998a","tid":2395274,"uid":390850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f75b81b76426a09465e77cd0ef984c02c61a2b","tid":2395274,"uid":154243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T20:34:51.000Z","msg":"係咪荷爾蒙問題呀？<br />\n我完咗A酸年半左右黎M前都會出痘<br />\n不過keep住搽A酸藥膏就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"我都懷疑係<br />\n荷爾蒙問題唔知可以點搞<br />\n我都係M前會出下巴或者腮位，以加出少左<br />\n但左右臉仲係會生唔停<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下絲打A酸藥膏係醫生嘅？"},{"pid":"12967c023bd2ad8abdc722e6bbfcfed3b905db9b","tid":2395274,"uid":390850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52a2159d692633ac1cbf71d5b2ef4502fd37746a","tid":2395274,"uid":209522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T21:04:16.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪對奶/蛋個啲敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前個情況同你一樣 又係食完一段時間後復發<br />\n之後我去做左個IgG食物敏感測試<br />\n之後發現原來對奶/蛋類嚴重敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住就開始戒 半年後就好好多 <br />\n有時口痕會買杯奶茶飲 <br />\n第二日有機會生暗瘡 不過都係啲細粒野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比之前好左好多<br />\n建議樓主都可以試吓 起碼知道有咩食得有咩唔食得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"巴打係邊間做個test啊<br />\n係咪要抽好多血(少淆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好鬼鐘意食海鮮同飲奶茶<br />\n希望我免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7b7f7e9be4173860c223c5b45c279cff6caa86","tid":2395274,"uid":209522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12967c023bd2ad8abdc722e6bbfcfed3b905d