ssets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b06c26702cfb0c1f5bc8e8a8e5c57547628b17c","tid":2395274,"uid":208402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁少都話復發"},{"pid":"9354ca0123eb88b0851fe9ea8d205bfdb5da2d4f","tid":2395274,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"Keep住低劑量就可以 我有朋友自己去買a酸口服 keep住低劑量食左半年 完全無事 同時keep住食護肝"},{"pid":"d0b7a3ac10dbcc9fe4cecbf6d88718558c541570","tid":2395274,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係試曬都唔得<br />\n但我A酸係因為食到好唔舒服好快放棄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />十幾年都斷唔到<br />\n<br />\n結果發現其實食B雜+zinc (連vitamin c)反而可以正常番"}]}